{"tid":493099,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【比iX更貴】LG推限量豪華智慧手機","createTime":"2017-12-08T07:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T10:54:53.000Z","uid":48628,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e543be0f2e89389ec9c1dd9f7883ab83258b76","tid":493099,"uid":48628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/155811_f91085bbe3d208558582dabee25478fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F155811_f91085bbe3d208558582dabee25478fa.jpg&h=261d318a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果史上最貴iPhone X需求熱烈更甚預期，惹得其他同業眼紅，如今南韓樂金電子（LG Electronics）也打算跟風推出高價位豪華版智慧手機，搶攻高階市場消費者荷包，售價甚至比iPhone X還高！<br />\n《韓聯社》、ZDNET等外媒報導，樂金電子12月稍後將推出旗下第1款豪華智慧機LG SIGNATURE Edition，限量300支，售價可能達200萬韓元（約5.92萬元台幣），比iPhone X南韓訂價163萬韓元（約4.83萬元台幣）更勝一籌。<br />\n「LG SIGNATURE（璽印）」原為樂金主打高端家電的品牌，這是首次跨足智慧手機產品。據樂金表示，將為這款豪華手機配置專門保固維修人員，且可依客戶要求在手機上刻印文字。<br />\n<br />\nLG SIGNATURE Edition機身為氧化鋯陶瓷材質，防刮耐磨能力強，配備6吋OLED FullVision螢幕，以及F1.6大光圈雙後置鏡頭，與樂金最新旗艦機V30相同。<br />\n此外，LG SIGNATURE Edition內建容量達256GB，可儲存大量高畫質影片、相片及音樂。耳機則採丹麥經品品牌Bang &amp; Olufsen，支援藍芽耳機。<br />\n在軟體方面，這款限量版豪華機將搭載Android最新版作業系統Oreo，支援LG Pay；LG Pay為樂金自行開發的行動支付平台，除感應支付外，也支援傳統信用卡磁條刷卡。（劉利貞／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171208/1255339/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171208%2F1255339%2F&d=UYGkvbzWySGVpgnXueqqfJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=b264dce1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171208%2F1255339%2F&h=a218f211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171208/1255339/</a>"},{"pid":"7c17aef45f8aed1044c32b5290834c2b95f4fe55","tid":493099,"uid":48628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" cla